<p><a href="http://strawberryjellyfish.com/wordpress-plugin-jellyfish-counter-widget/"><strong>Jellyfish Counter Widget</strong></a> is an odometer style counter widget which displays either a static value or animates to a set total.</p>
<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/so-mobile-map-widget/"><strong>SO Mobile Map Widget</strong></a> adds a mobile-optimised Google Static Map Image with a colored pin centered on a destination of your choosing.</p>
<h3>Updated plugins</h3>
<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/hotspots/"><strong>HotSpots</strong></a> draws a heat map of mouse clicks overlayed on your webpage allowing you to improve usability by analyzing user behaviour.</p>
